            <title>[MAHOUT-59] Create some examples of clustering well-known datasets</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-59</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The existing unit tests for clustering need to be augmented with examples from the literature which illustrate its correct operation on datasets which have known clusters present. See &lt;a href=&quot;http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/&lt;/a&gt; for some candidate datasets.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
